msg":"咁如果有狗守票站門口大抓捕點算<br />\n講緊唔係幾隻<br />\n係幾十幾百隻<br />\n<br />\n等記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a364e896b5ebc13edb44410b703c8069d6e694c","tid":1739764,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SCQjjEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSCQjjEv.jpg&h=23c935c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n稍為澄清下第七點"},{"pid":"f77fd79554f5a6d1505c8a8ca1a4a262e0d6b9b2","tid":1739764,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab7981896473dd464662adb2bc4f58ac1a904d70","tid":1739764,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"成個票箱唔見左都得<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇咁重投票 雖然係要去投但作用不大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"遊行無用，勇武無用，連儂牆無用，民意開始逆轉，開始攰，好想死，仲唔散係弱智，仲唔衝係嘥氣，條例已經死亡，警察已經內鬨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n建議你睇下"},{"pid":"1dfb82414118cadee12fd7971dd0518b7643ac0f","tid":1739764,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc9efa0b587b46179a6661c139c07b3d3bd1e415","tid":1739764,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d8b0d13196f4aee975df067b1ff97669cd8d528","tid":1739764,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"咁如果有狗守票站門口大抓捕點算<br />\n講緊唔係幾隻<br />\n係幾十幾百隻<br />\n<br />\n等記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:35:33.000Z","msg":"捕你啲乜？"},{"pid":"c7fa9b3ab311f2c0d05b5e6477a6216308ed49e1","tid":1739764,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qTVLfe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqTVLfe5.jpg&h=e3d9220d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFake news:《小心俾人拘留 導致無法投票》<br />\n<br />\n❗️其實理論上係唔會因為拘留而冇得投票❗️<br />\n要認清楚 同捍衛自己權利 <br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;&rsquo;遭懲教署囚禁或羈押的選民可在設於有關懲教署院 所的專用投票站投票。&lsquo;&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;&rsquo;而警署內亦會設立專用投票站，以供被其他執法機構羈押或拘留的選民投票。&lsquo;&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n囚禁：囚犯已定罪 服刑中<br />\n羈押：未定罪 不可保釋 待審訊<br />\n拘留：扣押48小時 <br />\n<br />\n以上三種都可以投票<br />\n<br />\n當然俾狗玩狗野嘅話 就冇辦法 要記低佢編號 時間等等 可要求聯絡律師 等律師做證及協助<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/pdf/2019DCE_Candidates_Briefing_Chairman_Speech_(Sup_Info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fpdf%2F2019DCE_Candidates_Briefing_Chairman_Speech_%28Sup_Info&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqLXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=a1ae5c6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/pdf/2019DCE_Candidates_Briefing_Chairman_Speech_(Sup_Info</a>).pdf"},{"pid":"0be7067b99b4372702f7d8a1ce2b722a0bc4c74b","tid":1739764,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c35605558d6900a64f6404c50e822d40456c56","tid":1739764,"uid":141785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:39:49.000Z","msg":"請問一下，洗唔洗攞埋「投票通知卡」去？定淨係身分證就OK？"},{"pid":"0cf619a60e73b3cfb873eea90b238bcec336e733","tid":1739764,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5c35605558d6900a64f6404c50e822d40456c56","tid":1739764,"uid":141785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:39:49.000Z","msg":"請問一下，洗唔洗攞埋「投票通知卡」去？定淨係身分證就OK？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:11:48.000Z","msg":"淨係身分證已經投到<br />\n你當拎埋冇壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(身分證係必須）"},{"pid":"73e5dd7f818c1561bc2c03de3b1d7b368a75eaef","tid":1739764,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cf619a60e73b3cfb873eea90b238bcec336e733","tid":1739764,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5c35605558d6900a64f6404c50e822d40456c56","tid":1739764,"uid":141785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:39:49.000Z","msg":"請問一下，洗唔洗攞埋「投票通知卡」去？定淨係身分證就OK？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:11:48.000Z","msg":"淨係身分證已經投到<br />\n你當拎埋冇壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(身分證係必須）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"如果你怕自己唔識去票站<br />\n或者唔記得票站係邊<br />\n我建議你拎埋出門口"},{"pid":"05311b462671bfa5fb2dcb4d9ec309e1edfb8f7b","tid":1739764,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc9efa0b587b46179a6661c139c07b3d3bd1e415","tid":1739764,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d8b0d13196f4aee975df067b1ff97669cd8d528","tid":1739764,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"咁如果有狗守票站門口大抓捕點算<br />\n講緊唔係幾隻<br />\n係幾十幾百隻<br />\n<br />\n等記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:35:33.000Z","msg":"捕你啲乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:17:17.000Z","msg":"機率好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過埋大一役之後<br />\n依家真&middot;全世界幾十億人口睇住香港"}]}